"title": "4342: jewels",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4342",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Precious stones, prized for their beauty and value are mentioned frequently in Scripture.</p>\n<h2>The breastpiece of the high priest was set with twelve jewels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15-Exod28:21\">EXO 28:15–28:21</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:8-Exod39:14\">EXO 39:8–39:14</a></p>\n<h2>The king of Tyre is depicted as having been adorned with jewels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:11-Ezek28:13\">EZK 28:11–28:13</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The new Jerusalem is described as being constructed of jewels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:18-Rev21:21\">REV 21:18–21:21</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Jewels in royal crowns</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:30\">2SA 12:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr20:2\">1CH 20:2</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:16\">ZEC 9:16</a></p>\n<h2>Jewels acquired through trade</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:22\">EZK 27:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:2\">1KI 10:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:1\">2CH 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:10-1Kgs10:11\">1KI 10:10–10:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:9-2Chr9:10\">2CH 9:9–9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:12\">REV 18:11–18:12</a></p>\n<h2>Wisdom is said to be more precious than jewels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:10-Prov8:11\">PRO 8:10–8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:12-Job28:19\">JOB 28:12–28:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:15\">PRO 3:13–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:15\">PRO 20:15</a></p>\n<h2>Jewels mentioned elsewhere in Scripture</h2>\n<h3>Carnelian</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:3\">REV 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:20\">REV 21:20</a></p>\n<h3>Chrysolite</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:9\">EZK 10:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:14\">SNG 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:16\">EZK 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:6\">DAN 10:6</a></p>\n<h3>Coral</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:16\">EZK 27:16</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Emeralds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:3\">REV 4:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jasper</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:3\">REV 4:3</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Onyx</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:9-Exod28:14\">EXO 28:9–28:14</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:6-Exod39:7\">EXO 39:6–39:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:10-Gen2:12\">GEN 2:10–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:1-Exod25:7\">EXO 25:1–25:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:4-Exod35:9\">EXO 35:4–35:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:27\">EXO 35:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:2\">1CH 29:2</a></p>\n<h3>Pearls</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:6\">MAT 7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:45-Matt13:46\">MAT 13:45–13:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:9-1Tim2:10\">1TI 2:9–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:4\">REV 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:11-Rev18:12\">REV 18:11–18:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:15-Rev18:17\">REV 18:15–18:17</a></p>\n<h3>Rubies</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:10\">PRO 31:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:11-Isa54:12\">ISA 54:11–54:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:7\">LAM 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:16\">EZK 27:16</a></p>\n<h3>Sapphires</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:11\">ISA 54:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:9-Exod24:10\">EXO 24:9–24:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:5-Job28:6\">JOB 28:5–28:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:14\">SNG 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:7\">LAM 4:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek1:26\">EZK 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:1\">EZK 10:1</a></p>\n<h3>Turquoise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:16\">EZK 27:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:2\">1CH 29:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:11\">ISA 54:11</a></p>",
